    "\n",
    "## Part 1 — Data Cleaning and Transformation (10 marks)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Dataset:** NYC Airbnb Open Data (`AB_NYC_2019.csv`)\n",
    "\n",
    "Tasks:\n",
